---
prompt:
  requires:
    - task_name
    - instructions
---
You are validating that the model can obey OpenAI's JSON-mode contract.

Task: {{task_name}}
Instructions: {{instructions}}

Respond with a single JSON object that contains:
- "task": copy of the task name
- "model_family": which OpenAI family you represent (gpt-4o, gpt-4.1, etc.)
- "status": always set to "ok" if you produced valid JSON
- "notes": array with at least one short bullet about JSON formatting
